defaultThe Association of School and College Leaders (ASCL) 
defaultrepresents 
defaultover 17,000 heads, principals, deputies, vice-principals, 
defaultassistant heads, business managers and other senior staff of maintained and independent schools and colleges throughout the UK. ASCL has members in more than 90 per cent of secondary schools and colleges of all types, responsible for the education of more 
defaultthan four million young people. This places the association in a unique position to consider this issue from the viewpoint of the leaders of secondary schools and of colleges.
